Package: CepalStatR
Title: Access to ECLAC (CEPALSTAT) Statistics via R
Version: 0.9.0
Authors@R: c(person("Henry", "Osorto", email = "henry.osorto@unah.edu.hn",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4334-9179")))
Description: Tools to explore metadata and retrieve indicators from the
    CEPALSTAT API of the Economic Commission for Latin America and the
    Caribbean (ECLAC), with support for tidy outputs, hierarchical indicator
    browsing, and basic visualizations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/Henry-Osorto/CepalStatR,
